  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Testing safety and tolerability of transcranial direct current stimulation (2 mA, 20
      minutes) in four different protocols:

      saline-soaked sponges electrode with electrode gel tap-water-soaked sponges
      tap-water-soaked-sponges + sham stimulation

      Outcome measures are tolerability (comfort rating questionnaire), impedances, skin
      elasticity
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
